Nora the Haunted
Master Hero (7 AP Build)
High Concept
An immensely powerful but deeply traumatized prodigy at the College of Winterhold, whose innate, Master-level grasp of Conjuration is a secret she desperately tries to suppress. She carries the souls of her parents in two black soul gems, a constant reminder of the childhood mistake that unleashed her terrifying talent.
Appearance
Based on A Fawn aesthetic, Nora has a slender, almost fragile build. She keeps her long, dark hair styled to partially hide her face, often with heavy bangs. Her large, expressive eyes are perpetually sad and averted, and she wears simple, dark clothing (often layered, non-traditional robes, chokers, etc.) to try and make herself as unnoticeable as possible. Around her neck, on two simple leather cords, hang two polished, unnervingly black soul gems that she touches compulsively when she's nervous.

